✅ 1. Define Your Core Features
Start small and build up. Some suggested features:

Public pages:

Home (list popular or trending movies)

Movie detail page

Search functionality

Authentication (protected routes):

Sign up / Log in / Log out

User profile (saved/favorite movies)

Extras (optional):

Filter by genre/year

Watch trailer (YouTube embed)

Pagination or infinite scroll

✅ 2. Choose the Right Stack
Here's a good tech stack for your project:

Frontend Framework: Next.js (with App Router)

Language: TypeScript

UI Framework: Tailwind CSS or ShadCN UI

Authentication: API ROUTE

API Source: TMDB API (easy to use for movie data)

State Management (optional): Zustand,

Database (for users): Mongodb

